高官問責，實行雙普選，減仇恨<br />\n<br />\n3.提升醫護個人裝備，立法限制病人行為<br />\n立即全面封關，賠償額提升到500萬<br />\n<br />\n根本你做少一樣，醫護都唔會開工"},{"pid":"3cb54ba030ffe2814889cf4f78911bc6033ef7a2","tid":1855464,"uid":268591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:23:45.000Z","msg":"支持，今次一定要做到真三罷！！"},{"pid":"b31ff81ada1a8a021149f03b964cf081ac89b650","tid":1855464,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:08:06.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"e07c18aeb250f5015b24a1031a4a787619acd228","tid":1855464,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:15:38.000Z","msg":"得把口支援有撚用咩"},{"pid":"9f1ae5c59bb238b1bd6bc545b32965645d712750","tid":1855464,"uid":38886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:16:11.000Z","msg":"齊上齊落"},{"pid":"453c571770627051491fe86d2f2566eaf0d93d90","tid":1855464,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:28:41.000Z","msg":"⚠️工會大全⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=fd0eb835\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n⚠️Group List⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike/1040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F1040&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=f49578fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkonstrike/1040</a><br />\n<br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會 | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\n頻道 <a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=b53939b2\" data-auto-link ta